// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2170 — Mass File Rename (stormous)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 78985075-1f87-564c-9cac-aa19160baa68

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
